NK041(di)023:1: // brgya bzhi'i cho ga 'dod don lhun grub ces bya ba bzhugs so //
NK041(di)023:2: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK041(di)023:3: phan bde'i mchog stsol dkon mchog rin chen gsum //
NK041(di)023:4: mi phyed dad pa'i gtsug gis gus mchod nas //
NK041(di)023:5: 'gro kun bdud bzhi la sogs 'jigs pa las //
NK041(di)023:6: bskyab phyir brgya bzhi'i cho ga mdor bsdus bkod //
NK041(di)023:7: de la sbyor ba yo byad 'byor tshad bsham pa /
NK041(di)023:8: dngos gzhi'i cho ga'i rim pa dang /
NK041(di)023:9: rjes lo rgyus kyi sgo nas phan yon bstan pa'o //
NK041(di)023:11: gang du bya ba'i sa phyogs rnams gtsang zhing dag par byas /
NK041(di)023:12: man+dala gyi gzhi la dri zhim gyis chag chag gdab /
NK041(di)023:13: der thig chen brgyad spyi ltar gdab pa'i lte ba nas zlum skor lngas bskor ba'i dbus mthing ga /
NK041(di)023:14: zlum skor dang po pad 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon /
NK041(di)023:18: de phyir ston pa'i phyag g.yas pa mchog sbyin gyi phyag rgya can bris /
NK041(di)023:19: phyag gi mkhrig ma'i thad du rin po che'am /
NK041(di)023:20: many+dzi'i khri'u la ston pa'i sku byin rlabs can phyag sor la phyogs par bzhugs so //
NK041(di)023:21: lte bar zangs gzhong sogs su 'bru sna'i ngar zan
NK041(di)023:22: la yon bdag gi glud khru gang ba skye mchod
NK041(di)023:23: dod cing gos rgyan gyis mtshan pa /
NK041(di)023:25: mo la glang ma'i shing byang lo grangs kyi khram btab pa /
NK041(di)023:26: rgyab tu 'dod gsol bris pa phrag g.yas la btsug pa /
NK041(di)023:31: gos dar sogs dkor cha du mas bskor nas /
NK041(di)023:32: mthe bong ma gtogs phyag sor bzhi'i rtse la 'jim pa sogs la 'bur du byas pa'am /
NK041(di)023:33: shing byang la bris pa sogs gang yang rung ba'i bdud bzhi'i gzugs bkod /
NK041(di)023:34: phung po'i bdud ser po mdzub mo /
NK041(di)023:35: 'chi bdag gi bdun nag po gung mo /
NK041(di)023:36: nyon mongs pa'i bdud dmar po srin lag /
NK041(di)023:37: lha'i bu'i bdud dkar po mathe'u chung la bkod /
NK041(di)023:38: man+dala gyi pad 'dab la phung po'i bdud sel phyir sku gdung s+aats+tsha brgya /
NK041(di)023:39: mu khyud gnyis pa la lha'i bu'i bdud sel phyir lha bshos brgya /
NK041(di)023:40: mu khyud gsum pa la nyon mongs pa'i bdud sel phyir mar me brgya /
NK041(di)023:41: mu khyud bzhi pa la 'chi bdag gi bdud sel phyir ngar glud brgya /
NK041(di)023:42: de rnams bskor thabs su mdzes par bkod /
NK041(di)023:44: mchog sbyin phyag rgya g.yas pa ru //
NK041(di)023:45: brgya bzhi'i yas dang rdzas bsags te //
NK041(di)023:46: phyag sor rtse la mgron bkug nas //
NK041(di)023:47: bdud bzhi bsal te mdangs dang ldan //
NK041(di)023:48: zhes gsungs pa ltar rim pa bzhin bkod /
NK041(di)023:49: gzhan yang de dag gi mthar /
NK041(di)023:50: spyi dang bye brag gi gtor mchod dang gser skyems la sogs pa yang bsham /
NK041(di)023:51: rang gi mdun nam phyogs gang bder dkon mchog spyi gtor dang /
NK041(di)023:52: chu gnyis nyer spyod lnga sogs dang /
NK041(di)023:53: 'thor rgyu'i me tog dang rol mo'i cha byad sogs
NK041(di)023:54: dgos pa'i yo byad thams cad tshogs par byas nas
NK041(di)023:55: bsham mo // de ltar bshams pa ni rab 'byor pa can gyi bshams tshul yin la /
NK041(di)023:56: gzhan la rdzas rnams lnga bcu'am /
NK041(di)023:57: nyer lnga sogs bshams la me long gcig gam /
NK041(di)023:58: gsum la gzugs brnyan shar ba'i grangs gis kha bskang
NK041(di)023:59: ba 'bring gi brgya bzhi ste gzugs brnyan gyi brgya
NK041(di)023:60: bzhi dang / tha ma rdzas re re tsam la brten nas brgya bsngo ba yin no //
NK041(di)023:62: gnyis pa cho ga'i rim pa la /
NK041(di)023:63: dpung bskyed pa'i rgyab chos dang /
NK041(di)023:64: cho ga dngos gzhi gnyis las /
NK041(di)023:65: dang po dge 'dun la chos ston drangs nas /
NK041(di)023:66: spyir dkon mchog la mchod pa dang /
NK041(di)023:68: bye brag skabs don dang sbyar ste /
NK041(di)023:69: tshe bsring ba la tshe mdo /
NK041(di)023:70: mi gtsang ba sel ba la rnam 'joms /
NK041(di)023:71: phur kha bzlog pa la gtsug tor gdugs dkar nag /
NK041(di)023:72: rims kha bzlog pa la ma mo'i bstod gzungs dang /
NK041(di)023:74: sa bdag gi gnod pa zhi ba la klu'i spang skor /
NK041(di)023:75: gshin don la spang skong phyag brgya pa /
NK041(di)023:76: dbang thang gso ba la dzam+b+ha la dang nor rgyun gyi gzungs 'don /
NK041(di)023:77: gza' skar ngan pa bzlog pa la sdong rgyan dang snang brgyad 'don /
NK041(di)023:78: gzhan yang chos skyong la bskang gsol dang /
NK041(di)023:79: sde brgyad 'byung po sogs la gser skyems gtor ma sogs dpung bskyed pa'i cho ga ci 'grub bya /
NK041(di)023:80: gnyis pa cho ga dngos gzhi'i rim pa la bcu gsum las /
NK041(di)023:82: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed dang tshad med pa bzhi bsgom pa sogs sngon du 'gro bas /
NK041(di)023:83: swa b+h+aa was stong par sbyang /
NK041(di)023:84: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi snying gar a las
NK041(di)023:85: zla ba'i steng du h'u ser po de'i 'od kyis
NK041(di)023:86: lus thams cad gang ba las rang nyid thub pa'i
NK041(di)023:87: dbang po'i skur gyur pa ni /
NK041(di)023:88: sku mdog gser btso ma lta bur zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK041(di)023:90: g.yon pa mnyam bzhag mdzad pa /
NK041(di)023:91: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK041(di)023:92: tshangs par spyod pa'i cha lugs can no //
NK041(di)023:93: mtshan dang dpe byad yongs su rdzogs shing /
NK041(di)023:94: chos gos rnam gsum gsol ba /
NK041(di)023:95: 'od dang 'od zer dpag tu med pa 'phro ba'i bdag nyid du bzhugs par gyur /
NK041(di)023:98: h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas ye shes sems dpa'i tshogs badz+ra sa ma ya dza dzahs spyan drangs /
NK041(di)023:99: mgon po thugs rje che ldan pa //
NK041(di)023:100: thams cad mkhyen pa ston pa po //
NK041(di)023:101: bsod nams yon tan rgya mtsho'i zhing //
NK041(di)023:102: de bzhin gshegs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)023:106: dzahmh'u ba hoh gnyis su med par gyur /
NK041(di)023:107: snying ga'i sa bon gyi mthar sngags kyi phreng bas bskor bar bsgoms la /
NK041(di)023:108: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)023:109: zhes bzlas pa ci nus bzlas la /
NK041(di)023:110: gnyis pa sku gdung rab gnas ni /
NK041(di)023:111: rang gi thugs ka'i 'od zer 'phros pas phyogs bcu'i
NK041(di)023:112: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad mdun
NK041(di)023:113: gyi nam mkhar gshegs par gyur /
NK041(di)023:114: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing /
NK041(di)023:116: ar+g+ham sogs kyis mchod cing bstod /
NK041(di)023:117: nam mkha'i lha tshogs rnams 'od zer gyi phung por gyur nas sku gdung la thim par gyur /
NK041(di)023:118: me tog dor zhing rten 'brel snying po bzlas nas s+aats+tsha la gtor /
NK041(di)023:119: sangs rgyas rjes su dran pa'i mdo yang 'don la shis brjod bya /
NK041(di)023:120: gsum pa tshogs bsags pa ni /
NK041(di)023:121: rab gnas bya ba'i tshogs rten nyid du mos so //
NK041(di)023:122: mchod bstod yan lag bdun pa bya zhing /
NK041(di)023:123: bsdu na bzang spyod las byung ba'i yan lag bdun pa tsam bya'o //
NK041(di)023:124: spyir bdag bskyed ni yi dam gang la byas kyang rung /
NK041(di)023:125: 'dir bstan cho ga ni yig rnying khungs ldan dpyad bzod pa dag las /
NK041(di)023:126: bdag bskyed nas tshogs bsags pa ni /
NK041(di)023:127: gong gi bsgrigs rim 'byung ba de ltar ro //
NK041(di)023:128: bzhi pa rdzas rnams byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK041(di)023:129: ra ya kha gis ma dag pa'i dngos po thams cad bsregs gtor bkrus te stong par bsam la /
NK041(di)023:131: bye brag tu sngags drug phyag drug gi byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK041(di)023:132: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i thal mo khong stong du snying gar sbyar te /
NK041(di)023:133: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+hah sarba d+harmahswab+h+aa wa shud+d+ho&ahamh lan gsum mam bdun brjod /
NK041(di)023:134: rdzas rnams rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK041(di)023:136: thal mo khong stong du sen mo rtse sprad pas tshig rnams bcag pa smin mtshams su bzhag la /
NK041(di)023:137: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK041(di)023:138: khe b+h+yah sarba th+aa kham ung+ga te s+pha ra na
NK041(di)023:139: i mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)023:140: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga zad mi shes pas nam mkha' gang bar bsam mo //
NK041(di)023:142: thal mo sbyar ba phyir bskyed /
NK041(di)023:143: mthe bong gnyis bsnol te kha'i thad kar bzhag /
NK041(di)023:144: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da l+ai ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK041(di)023:145: yo byad thams cad bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur par bsam mo //
NK041(di)023:147: g.yas rdo rje khu tshur bcing pa'i mdzub mo sgreng /
NK041(di)023:148: g.yon pa sa gnon byas la /
NK041(di)023:149: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta +aa ba lo ki te sam b+ha ra sam b+ha ra h'u /
NK041(di)023:150: yo byad thams cad so so'i bsam pa dang mthun par bsam mo //
NK041(di)023:152: g.yas rdo rje khu tshur snying gar bca' la /
NK041(di)023:153: g.yon mchog sbyin gyis snod 'degs pa'i tshul dang /
NK041(di)023:154: dz+ny+aa na a ba lo ki te na mahs man+ta
NK041(di)023:155: s+pha ra na rasmi b+ha ba sa ma ya ma
NK041(di)023:156: h+aa ma ni du ru du ru hri da ya
NK041(di)023:158: yo byad thams cad mgron rnams 'thab rtsod med par longs spyod par bsam mo //
NK041(di)023:160: lag gnyis kyi sor mo nang du bsnol nas mkhrig mar sbyar /
NK041(di)023:161: mthe bong gnyis gshibs te brkyangs pa spyi bor bskor la /
NK041(di)023:162: na mahs man+ta bu d+d+h+aa nam gra he shwa ri
NK041(di)023:163: pra b+ha dz+yo ti ni ma h+aa sa ma ya
NK041(di)023:164: s+w+aa h+aa / mgron rnams thams cad bdag nyid kyi dbang du gyur par bsam la /
NK041(di)023:165: de ltar sngags lan gsum mam bdun brjod pa'i phyag rgya bkrol ba na se gol bya'o //
NK041(di)023:167: bdag gi bsam pa'i stobs dang ni //
NK041(di)023:168: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sbyin stobs dang //
NK041(di)023:169: chos kyi dbyings kyi stobs rnams kyis //
NK041(di)023:170: 'phags pa rnams la mchod pa dang //
NK041(di)023:171: sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK041(di)023:172: don rnams gang dag bsam pa kun //
NK041(di)023:173: de dag thams cad ci rigs pa //
NK041(di)023:174: thogs pa med par 'byung gyur cig /
NK041(di)023:176: lnga pa mgron rnams spyan drang ba ni /
NK041(di)023:177: rol mo dbyangs dang bcas pas 'di skad do //
NK041(di)023:179: sangs rgyas rkang gnyis gtso ste bden pa'i mchog /
NK041(di)023:180: chos nyid chags dang bral te bden pa'i mchog /
NK041(di)023:181: dge 'dun 'dus pa'i gtso ste bden pa'i mchog /
NK041(di)023:182: bden pa'i mchog ni dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' //
NK041(di)023:183: dkon mchog bka' la mi nyan gang yang med //
NK041(di)023:184: srid pa'i rtse nas dmyal khams yan chad kyi //
NK041(di)023:185: mgron gyi rigs su gyur pa thams cad kun //
NK041(di)023:186: tshur byon bde gshegs rgyal ba'i bka' la nyon //
NK041(di)023:188: srid gsum 'di na su yang rung //
NK041(di)023:189: gnod par byed pa'i bgegs rigs rnams //
NK041(di)023:190: tshur byon rgyal ba'i bka' la nyon //
NK041(di)023:191: 'bul ba bdag gis ma nor la //
NK041(di)023:192: bzhes pa khyod kyis ma 'khrul cig /
NK041(di)023:193: 'chi bdag bdud dang phung po'i bdud //
NK041(di)023:194: nyon mongs bdud dang lha'i bu'i bdud //
NK041(di)023:195: bdud bzhi bdud kyi dmag dpung tshogs //
NK041(di)023:196: skye mched mu bzhi gnas dag nas //
NK041(di)023:198: dkon mchog bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK041(di)023:199: da lta nyid du gshegs su gsol //
NK041(di)023:200: sngon tshe lha dbang brgya byin ni //
NK041(di)023:201: 'chi bdag bdud kyis zin pa la //
NK041(di)023:202: bcom ldan rgyal ba sh+aaka thub kyis //
NK041(di)023:203: brgya bzhi'i sbyin pa btang ba yis //
NK041(di)023:204: lha dbang brgya byin bsnyun las thar //
NK041(di)023:205: da lta rgyu sbyor yon bdag la //
NK041(di)023:206: bdud bzhi'i khram kha bab pa dang //
NK041(di)023:207: lha 'dre'i dal kha zug pa dang //
NK041(di)023:208: mo ngan rmi ltas ngan pa dang //
NK041(di)023:209: 'byung bzhi'i bdud ni g.yos pa dang //
NK041(di)023:210: ngan pa thams cad bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK041(di)023:211: brgya bzhi'i yas dang rdzas bsags te //
NK041(di)023:213: skad cig tsam gyis 'dir gshegs la //
NK041(di)023:214: bcom ldan thub pa chen po yi //
NK041(di)023:215: phyag sor bzhi yi rtse la bzhugs //
NK041(di)023:218: dzahmh'u ba hoh rang rang gi gzugs dang gnyis su med par bzhugs par gyur /
NK041(di)023:219: drug pa rdzas rnams spyir bsngo ba ni /
NK041(di)023:221: sngon tshe rgyal ba shaka thub kyis //
NK041(di)023:222: lha dbang bsnyun gyis zin pa la //
NK041(di)023:223: mchog sbyin phyag rgya g.yas pa ru //
NK041(di)023:224: brgya bzhi'i yas dang rdzas bsags te //
NK041(di)023:225: phyag sor rtse la mgron bkug nas //
NK041(di)023:226: bdud bzhi bsal te mdangs dang ldan //
NK041(di)023:227: sngon gyi bden pas byin rlabs dang //
NK041(di)023:228: da lta rgyu sbyor yon bdag gis //
NK041(di)023:229: bsam sbyor dang bas bsham pa yi //
NK041(di)023:230: mchod sbyin glud gtor 'di bzhes la //
NK041(di)023:231: khram la bab na khram kha sgyur //
NK041(di)023:232: shwa la bab na shwa rdel gtor //
NK041(di)023:233: rtsis la bab na rtsis rdel phyung //
NK041(di)023:234: rgyan la bab na rgyan kha spos //
NK041(di)023:235: bzung ba thong la bcings pa khrol //
NK041(di)023:236: bdud kyi zhags pa slar sdus shig /
NK041(di)023:238: lha'i bu'i bdud ni dkar po khyod //
NK041(di)023:239: shes bya'i sgrib pa dag las byung //
NK041(di)023:240: nyon mongs bdud ni dmar po khyod //
NK041(di)023:241: dug lnga nyon mongs sgrib las byung //
NK041(di)023:242: 'chi bdag bdud ni nag po khyod //
NK041(di)023:243: bag chags las kyi sgrib las byung //
NK041(di)023:244: phung po'i bdud ni ser po khyod //
NK041(di)023:245: rnam smin las kyi sgrib las byung //
NK041(di)023:246: da lta rgyu sbyor yon bdag gi //
NK041(di)023:247: sgrib pa rnam bzhi sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK041(di)023:248: mchod dang sbyin pa'i las bya yis //
NK041(di)023:249: mchod pa'i zhing ni dkon mchog gsum //
NK041(di)023:250: sbyin pa'i mgron ni bgegs kyi tshogs //
NK041(di)023:251: mchod rdzas mar me zhal zas dang //
NK041(di)023:252: lan chags glud dang gtor ma yis //
NK041(di)023:253: bsod nams ye shes tshogs bsags pas //
NK041(di)023:254: nyon mongs sgrib dang shes bya'i sgrib //
NK041(di)023:255: bag chags sgrib dang rnam smin sgrib //
NK041(di)023:256: sgrib pa rnam bzhi sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK041(di)023:257: mchod sbyin gtor ma rgya chen 'dis //
NK041(di)023:258: lha bdud shes bya'i sgrib las thar //
NK041(di)023:259: snang byed gsal ba'i mar me 'dis //
NK041(di)023:260: nyon mongs dug lnga'i sgrib las thar //
NK041(di)023:261: lan chags srog glud 'di bsngosa pas //
NK041(di)023:262: 'chi bdag bag chags sgrib las thar //
NK041(di)023:263: bsod nams tshogs su 'di bsngo pas //
NK041(di)023:264: phung bdud rnam smin sgrib las thar //
NK041(di)023:265: bdud bzhi sel ba'i gto dpyad 'dis //
NK041(di)023:266: sngon tshe rgyal ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK041(di)023:267: da lta rgyu sbyor yon bdag gi //
NK041(di)023:268: bar chad rkyen rnams bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK041(di)023:270: grib dang mi gtsang dri ma'i tshogs //
NK041(di)023:271: tshogs gnyis bsags pas dag par byed //
NK041(di)023:272: bdud kyi gtso bo bdud chen bzhi //
NK041(di)023:273: cho ga snang gsal brgya bzhi ste //
NK041(di)023:275: bdud chen bzhi po rab tu sel //
NK041(di)023:276: nad kyi gtso bo 'du ba bzhi //
NK041(di)023:278: gzugs kyi phung po 'jig par byed //
NK041(di)023:279: de ni tshangs pa sman gyis sel //
NK041(di)023:280: bgegs kyi gtso bo bdud chen bzhi //
NK041(di)023:281: bar chad rkyen dang glo bur byed //
NK041(di)023:282: de dag mchod sbyin brgya bzhi yi //
NK041(di)023:283: cho gas gnod byed sel bar byed //
NK041(di)023:285: dngos dang gzugs brnyan ting 'dzin gyis //
NK041(di)023:286: brgya bzhi byin gyis brlabs nas ni //
NK041(di)023:287: bdud chen bzhi la 'bul lags na //
NK041(di)023:288: dgyes pa'i tshul gyis bzhes mdzod la //
NK041(di)023:289: bzung ba thong la bcings pa khrol //
NK041(di)023:290: phyin chad gnod pa ma byed par //
NK041(di)023:291: srid zhi'i mgron dang ldan gyur cig /
NK041(di)023:292: ces bsngo zhing glud gtor rnams kha 'bar ma'i sngags kyis yid ches par bsngo zhing /
NK041(di)023:293: sngags brgya rtsa rdzogs nas phrin las gsol bar bya'o //
NK041(di)023:294: skabs 'dir gser skyems dang gtong ma bsngo ba yig rnying gi dkyus na mi gsal yang /
NK041(di)023:295: bar skabs kyi lag len du 'dug pas spro na zur du blta'o //
NK041(di)023:296: bdun pa bye brag tu bsngo ba ni /
NK041(di)023:298: mtho ba rnams ni mar gson cig /
NK041(di)023:299: dma' ba rnams kyang yar gson cig /
NK041(di)023:300: che ba rnams kyis ma bkyon cig /
NK041(di)023:301: chung ba rnams kyang ma 'khong zhig /
NK041(di)023:302: rgyu sbyor yon gyi bdag po la //
NK041(di)023:303: bdud kyi dmag dpung byung ba'i tshe //
NK041(di)023:304: yon bdag glud du brgya bzhi 'bul //
NK041(di)023:305: s+aats+tsha brgya dang snang gsal brgya //
NK041(di)023:306: gtor ma brgya dang ngar glud brgya //
NK041(di)023:307: bdud chen bzhi yi phyag tu 'bul //
NK041(di)023:308: sku gsung thugs kyi glud du 'bul //
NK041(di)023:309: bdud kyi dmag dpung bzlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)023:310: a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti she pri ba sarba a pa na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)023:311: zhes pas so sor gser skyems mchod /
NK041(di)023:312: yon bdag gam gzhan gyis kyang rung ste /
NK041(di)023:313: nas nag gis brab pa sogs bya'o //
NK041(di)023:315: mtho ba rnams ni mar gson cig /
NK041(di)023:316: dma' ba rnams kyang yar gson cig /
NK041(di)023:317: che ba rnams kyi ma bkyon cig /
NK041(di)023:318: chung ba rnams kyang ma 'khong cig /
NK041(di)023:319: de ring rgyu sbyor yon bdag la //
NK041(di)023:320: de bzhin du mtho ba rnams ni zhes tshig rkang
NK041(di)023:321: lnga po 'di 'og ma kun gyi thog mar sbyar
NK041(di)023:322: ro // gshin rje'i dmag dpung byung ba'i tshe //
NK041(di)023:323: yon bdag glud du brgya bzhi 'bul //
NK041(di)023:324: s+aa ts+tsha brgya dang snang gsal brgya //
NK041(di)023:325: gtor ma brgya dang ngar glud brgya //
NK041(di)023:326: gshin rje rnams kyi phyag tu 'bul //
NK041(di)023:327: sku gsung thugs kyi glud du 'bul //
NK041(di)023:328: gshin rje'i dmag tshogs bzlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)023:329: a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti ya ma r+aa dza sarba a pa na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)023:331: mtho ba rnams ni sogs gong ltar 'gres /
NK041(di)023:332: gnod sbyin dmag dpung byung ba'i tshe //
NK041(di)023:333: yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma gnod sbyin rnams kyi sku
NK041(di)023:334: gsung gnod sbyin a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti yak+sha g+r+ai
NK041(di)023:335: wa sarba a pa na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)023:338: tshangs pa'i dmag dpung byung ba'i tshe //
NK041(di)023:339: yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma tshangs pa sku gsung tshangs
NK041(di)023:340: pa'i a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti bra h+ma sarba a
NK041(di)023:344: srin po'i yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma srin po sku
NK041(di)023:345: gsung srin po'i a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti rak+sha sarba
NK041(di)023:347: rgyal po'i yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma rgyal po'i dmag
NK041(di)023:348: tshogs sku gsung rgyal po'i a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti
NK041(di)023:351: the'u rang yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma the'u rang sku
NK041(di)023:352: gsung the'u rang a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti kar sha
NK041(di)023:355: gza' skar yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma gza' skar sku
NK041(di)023:356: gsung gza' skar a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti r+aa hu
NK041(di)023:359: sa bdag klu gnyan yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma sa
NK041(di)023:360: bdag klu gnyan sku gsung sa bdag klu gnyan dmag
NK041(di)023:361: dpung a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti n+aa ga r+aa dza
NK041(di)023:362: sarba a kye / mtho ba rnams 'gres /
NK041(di)023:364: s+aats+tsha gtor ma ma mo rnams sku gsung a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti ma ma rak+mo sarba a kye /
NK041(di)023:366: mi yi yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma mi yi dmag
NK041(di)023:367: dpung sku gsung mi yi a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti
NK041(di)023:370: me lha'i 'jigs pa yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma me
NK041(di)023:371: lha rnams sku gsung me lha'i dmag a pa ra
NK041(di)023:372: tsakra h+r+aihti ra sarba a kye /
NK041(di)023:374: chu lha'i 'jigs yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma chu lha
NK041(di)023:375: rnams sku gsung chu lha'i dmag a pa ra tsakra
NK041(di)023:378: sa lha'i 'jigs yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma sa lha
NK041(di)023:379: rnams sku gsung sa lha'i dmag a pa ra tsakra
NK041(di)023:382: rlung lha'i 'jigs yon bdag s+aats+tsha gtor ma rlung lha
NK041(di)023:383: rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi rlung lha'i dmag tshogs
NK041(di)023:384: bzlog tu gsol // a pa ra tsakra h+r+aihti ya sarba a pa na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)023:385: zhes brjod cing gser skyems 'thor la nas nag gis brab nas rol mo dang bcas pa bya'o //
NK041(di)023:386: brgyad pa glud bsngo ba ni /
NK041(di)023:387: phyag mthil gyi glud chen gtso bor dmigs te /
NK041(di)023:389: stong pa'i ngang las yon bdag gi 'dra glud mdzes shing brjid pa yid du 'ong ba /
NK041(di)023:390: smra mkhas shing shes rig bkra ba /
NK041(di)023:391: 'jam pa'i gos dang mdzes pa'i rgyan gyis spras pa /
NK041(di)023:392: mkho rgu'i dkor nor bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan par gyur /
NK041(di)023:393: rgyas par sngags drug phyag drug gam /
NK041(di)023:394: bsdu nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgyas byin gyis brlabs la /
NK041(di)023:396: srid gsum 'di na gang yang rung //
NK041(di)023:397: bgegs kyi rigs su gyur pa gang //
NK041(di)023:398: tshur gshegs rgyal ba'i bka' la nyon //
NK041(di)023:399: rin chen 'bru mchog ngar gyi mi //
NK041(di)023:400: nam mkha'i sems la zho sha'i snying //
NK041(di)023:401: dung gi rus la bswe yi sha /
NK041(di)023:402: mtshal gyi khrag la me yi drod //
NK041(di)023:403: rlung gi dbugs la chu yi khams //
NK041(di)023:404: zer mo'i skra la mu tig klad //
NK041(di)023:405: long thang mig la mgron bu'i so //
NK041(di)023:406: le brgan lce la dbang po'i lag /
NK041(di)023:407: zangs lcags rkang la dar zab gos //
NK041(di)023:408: rin chen rgyan cha dkor cha'i nor //
NK041(di)023:409: phung khams skye mched dag dang ldan //
NK041(di)023:410: gzugs mdzes gom stobs lams se lam //
NK041(di)023:411: smra mkhas ngag snyan kyu ru ru //
NK041(di)023:412: sems ni rtog dpyod hrigs se hrig /
NK041(di)023:413: bcas bcas de ni brdar brdar nas //
NK041(di)023:414: skyes pa dmag la chas pa 'dra //
NK041(di)023:415: brgyan brgyan de ni spungs spungs nas //
NK041(di)023:416: na chung bag mar chas pa 'dra //
NK041(di)023:417: btsal btsal de ni bsags bsags nas //
NK041(di)023:418: rgyal po'i bang mdzod dbye ba 'dra //
NK041(di)023:419: de 'dra'i glud bzang ngo mtshar can //
NK041(di)023:420: mi bas glud dga' bzhes su gsol //
NK041(di)023:421: lan chags bskang zhing bu lon byang //
NK041(di)023:422: gnod pa'i bsam sbyor ngan pa sgyur //
NK041(di)023:423: dus min 'chi ba'i rkyen rnams sgyur //
NK041(di)023:424: chag che nyam nga zhi ba dang //
NK041(di)023:425: tshe dbang longs spyod rgyas par mdzod //
NK041(di)023:427: sngon gyi skyes rabs brjod de 'bul ba ni /
NK041(di)023:429: sngon tshe rgyal ba sh+aaka thub kyis //
NK041(di)023:430: mchog sbyin phyag rgya g.yas pa ru //
NK041(di)023:431: phyag sor rtse la bdud bzhi bos //
NK041(di)023:432: mgron du bkug nas mchod sbyin bsngosa //
NK041(di)023:433: rgyu sbyor yon gyi bdag po ni //
NK041(di)023:434: dad can phyag gi mthil du bzhag /
NK041(di)023:435: gces par mdzad nas dbang bskur bas //
NK041(di)023:436: sgrib pa bzhi las gyur pa yi //
NK041(di)023:437: bdud bzhi bsal te mdangs dang ldan //
NK041(di)023:438: sngon tshe bden pa'i byin rlabs ltar //
NK041(di)023:439: da lta bdag dang yon bdag gi //
NK041(di)023:440: gzugs glud phyag gi mthil du bzhag /
NK041(di)023:441: mtha' mar brgya bzhi'i rdzas kyis bskor //
NK041(di)023:442: bdud bzhi phyag sor rtse la bzhag /
NK041(di)023:443: byin gyis brlabs shing bsngosa te 'bul //
NK041(di)023:444: bden pa chen po'i bka' la nyon //
NK041(di)023:445: skye mched mu bzhi'i gnas su dengs //
NK041(di)023:447: dgu pa smon lam btab pa ni /
NK041(di)023:449: brgya bzhi'i mchod sbyin rgya chen po bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs su bsngo bar bagyi'o //
NK041(di)023:450: sku gdung s+aats+tsha btab pa'i byin rlabs kyis sems can
NK041(di)023:451: thams cad dge ba bcu la spyod par gyur cig
NK041(di)023:452: / mi dge ba bcu spangs bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)023:453: mar me brgya phul ba'i bsod nams kyis sems can thams cad ma rig pa'i mun pa bsal nas /
NK041(di)023:454: ye shes lnga'i don rtogs par gyur cig /
NK041(di)023:455: gtor ma brgya phul ba'i bsod nams kyis sems can
NK041(di)023:456: thams cad mu ge'i bskal pa las thar bar gyur
NK041(di)023:457: cig / ngar glud brgya phul ba'i bsod nams kyis
NK041(di)023:458: sems can thams cad bgegs kyis gnod pa'i lan chags
NK041(di)023:459: dang bu lon thams cad byang bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)023:460: mdo sde zab mo bton pa'i byin rlabs kyis sems
NK041(di)023:461: can thams cad rtag tu chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK041(di)023:462: bar gyur cig / brgya bzhi phul ba'i dge ba'i
NK041(di)023:463: rtsa ba 'dis bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon gyi bdag
NK041(di)023:464: po 'khor dang bcas pa'i lan chags bu lon thams
NK041(di)023:466: tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK041(di)023:467: kyi go 'phang rin po che thob par gyur cig
NK041(di)023:469: bcu pa zlog pa bya ba ni /
NK041(di)023:471: mchod sbyin brgya bzhi'i bden stobs kyi //
NK041(di)023:472: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag la //
NK041(di)023:473: yas kyi bdud g.yos brgya bzhis zlog /
NK041(di)023:474: mas kyi sri langs brgya bzhis zlog /
NK041(di)023:475: pha bu'i rgan sri ma bu'i byur sri byis pa'i
NK041(di)023:476: chung sri chos zor bor zor gtad khram byad stems
NK041(di)023:477: lo kag zla kag zhag kag za kag ngan pa
NK041(di)023:478: zlog gza' skar ngan pa thams cad zlog /
NK041(di)023:479: rbad 'dre rbod gtong mi yi shi kha nor phyugs
NK041(di)023:480: god kha dgra kha rkun kha skye bo'i ya ga
NK041(di)023:481: ngan pa sde brgyad 'byung pos gnod pa zlog /
NK041(di)023:482: gnam gyi 'ju thag chad pa sa yi rten phur
NK041(di)023:483: phyung pa rmi lam mtshan ma ngan pa rgya yi
NK041(di)023:484: gtsug lag ngan pa bod kyi mo rtsis ngan pa
NK041(di)023:485: ngan dgu rtsub bcu thams cad zlog /
NK041(di)023:486: chags che nyam nga thams cad brgya bzhis zlog /
NK041(di)023:487: ces brjod cing thal rdeb bya'o //
NK041(di)023:488: de nas bdud bzhi'i gzugs brnyan dang glud sogs yas
NK041(di)023:489: rdzas rnams gnas khang gi sgo dang nye bar dpags
NK041(di)023:491: nyon cig ma lus bgegs kyi tshogs //
NK041(di)023:492: lha klu gnod sbyin la sogs pa //
NK041(di)023:495: de ring yon bdag 'khor bcas la //
NK041(di)023:496: gnod par byed pa gang yang rung //
NK041(di)023:497: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK041(di)023:498: bzung ba las ni thar bar mdzod //
NK041(di)023:499: bcings pa las ni grol bar mdzod //
NK041(di)023:500: rin dang glud du gtor ma longs //
NK041(di)023:501: bdag gis de ring khyod mchod do //
NK041(di)023:502: song zhig bgegs chen 'gro bar gyis //
NK041(di)023:503: phyin chad de ltar ma byed cig /
NK041(di)023:504: khyod kyi stobs dang rtsal mthong na //
NK041(di)023:505: khyod kyis bgegs chen mi nus min //
NK041(di)023:506: khyod ni lha yi sprul pa ste //
NK041(di)023:507: sngon chad mchod sbyin ma thob bar //
NK041(di)023:508: de ring bdag gis khyod mchod kyis //
NK041(di)023:509: me tog phreng ba spos dang dri //
NK041(di)023:510: mar me zhal zas 'di rnams kyis //
NK041(di)023:511: bgegs kyi rgyal po 'gro bar gyis //
NK041(di)023:512: sngon gyi lan chags yod na yang //
NK041(di)023:513: mchod sbyin 'di yis bral bar mdzod //
NK041(di)023:514: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' dang ni //
NK041(di)023:515: dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes pa yis //
NK041(di)023:516: gnod par gyur pa ma legs kyang //
NK041(di)023:517: bgegs chen khyod ni da songs shig /
NK041(di)023:518: rdo rje chen po mchog 'dzin pa'i //
NK041(di)023:519: bka' las gang du 'da' ba ni //
NK041(di)023:520: rdo rje 'dzin pas myur du spangs //
NK041(di)023:521: spangs pas sems can chen po ste //
NK041(di)023:522: ji srid 'khor ba'i spyod yul du //
NK041(di)023:523: ngan song gsum por ltung nas kyang //
NK041(di)023:524: shin tu mi bzad cho nges 'debs //
NK041(di)023:525: bdag nyid chen po sangs rgyas bka' //
NK041(di)023:526: tshig las 'das na rdul du brlag /
NK041(di)023:527: de bas bgegs chen khyod songs la //
NK041(di)023:528: dam tshig las ni ma 'da' zhig /
NK041(di)023:530: bcu gnyis pa gshegs su gsol ba ni //
NK041(di)023:531: de nas yas rnams nad pa dang yon bdag la lan gsum bskor la /
NK041(di)023:532: des nad gdon dang chags che nyam nga thams cad blangs shing rang gnas su song bar bsam /
NK041(di)023:533: spos dang gser skyems kyis sna drangs te /
NK041(di)023:534: phyogs ngan sogs gang du btang ba'i sar khyer bar bya'o //
NK041(di)023:536: bgegs kyi rgyal po bdud chen bzhi //
NK041(di)023:537: bden pa chen po'i bka' la nyon //
NK041(di)023:538: lha bdud bya ba'i dkar po khyod //
NK041(di)023:539: ci yang med pa'i gnas su dengs //
NK041(di)023:540: 'chi bdag bdud ni nag po khyod //
NK041(di)023:541: nam mkha' mtha' yas gnas su dengs //
NK041(di)023:542: nyon mongs bdud ni dmar po khyod //
NK041(di)023:543: rnam shes mtha' yas gnas su dengs //
NK041(di)023:544: phung po'i bdud ni ser po khyod //
NK041(di)023:545: yod min med min gnas su dengs //
NK041(di)023:546: sgrib pa rnam bzhi las byung ba'i //
NK041(di)023:547: bdud kyi rgyal po 'khor dang bcas //
NK041(di)023:549: skye mched rigs bzhi'i gnas su dengs //
NK041(di)023:550: sa ma ya pra be sha ya dza dzah zhes pas yas rnams dor /
NK041(di)023:551: shes rab snying po 'don cing gzungs sngags brjod /
NK041(di)023:552: srung ba'i ched du rab tu gnas shing 'khor gsum mi dmigs pa'i rgyas gdab /
NK041(di)023:553: nang du log nas mdo 'don pa de'i snying po
NK041(di)023:554: gro ga'am shog bur bris pa'i gzungs gzhugs su bcug
NK041(di)023:555: pa'i s+aats+tsha bcu gnas khang gi phyogs mtshams bcu la
NK041(di)023:556: so sor srung ba'i don du gzhug go //
NK041(di)023:557: rten 'brel snying po bzlas pa'i me tog 'thor zhing brtan bzhugs dang shis brjod bya'o //
NK041(di)023:558: bcu gsum pa slar yang mtha' rgyas par bya ba'i phyir /
NK041(di)023:559: dkon mchog gsum la mchod pa bzang du bshams shing phul la /
NK041(di)023:561: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK041(di)023:562: bdag cag yon mchod 'khor dang bcas //
NK041(di)023:563: lha bu'i bdud kyi g.yul ngo las //
NK041(di)023:564: da ni rgyal lo rnam par rgyal //
NK041(di)023:565: nyon mongs bdud kyi g.yul ngo las //
NK041(di)023:566: da ni rgyal lo rnam par rgyal //
NK041(di)023:567: phung po'i bdud kyi g.yul ngo las //
NK041(di)023:568: da ni rgyal lo rnam par rgyal //
NK041(di)023:569: 'chi bdag bdud kyi g.yul ngo las //
NK041(di)023:570: da ni rgyal lo rnam par rgyal //
NK041(di)023:571: zhes brjod cing las kyi rjes bsdu ba dang /
NK041(di)023:572: bkra shis kyi tshigs bcad rgya cher brjod cing me
NK041(di)023:573: tog gi char dbab pa sogs kyis bde legs su
NK041(di)023:574: khyab par bya'o // gsum pa lo rgyus gyi sgo nas phan yon bstan pa ni /
NK041(di)023:575: sngon lha'i dbang po brgya byin bsnyun gyis zin pa la /
NK041(di)023:576: ston pa bcom ldan 'das la gsol ba btab pas /
NK041(di)023:577: bcom ldan 'das kyis bdud bzhis zin par mkhyen nas rgya bzhi'i cho ga 'di mdzad pas /
NK041(di)023:578: brgya byin bsnyun las thar nas bde ba la bkod /
NK041(di)023:579: de ltar phan yon chen po dang ldan pa'i cho
NK041(di)023:580: ga rdzas las brgya bzhir mtshan du grags pa de
NK041(di)023:581: nyid 'phags pa klu sgrub kyi phyag tu babs pas
NK041(di)023:582: / rdo rje gdan gyi ka gdan spre'u 'dra ba
NK041(di)023:583: la gter du sbas pa pan+di ta lnga brgyas bton
NK041(di)023:584: nas gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la
NK041(di)023:585: / bstsal / des bod du bsnams nas gzhan phan gyi phrin las rgya cher mdzad pa'o //
NK041(di)023:586: cho ga dela'ang mdo lugs dang sngags lugs zhes tha dad du yod pa las /
NK041(di)023:587: 'di nyid mdo ltar grags pa'i lugs so //
NK041(di)023:588: gzhan sngags lugs gshin rje nag po'i rgyud las btus pa /
NK041(di)023:590: o rgyan chen po sogs brgyud par grags pa'i yi
NK041(di)023:591: ge zur pa'i bla ma gong ma rnams kyis phyag
NK041(di)023:592: len du mdzad pa zhig snang ba ni /
NK041(di)023:593: yi ge rnying pa na gsal bar 'dug pa las shes so //
NK041(di)023:594: de lta bu'i cho ga 'dis ban bon gyi phur kha zug pa dang /
NK041(di)023:597: skye bo'i ya ga ngan pa dang /
NK041(di)023:598: mi'i shi kha bye ba dang /
NK041(di)023:599: phyugs nad god kha byung ba dang /
NK041(di)023:600: yul du nad yams dar ba dang /
NK041(di)023:601: khyad par rgyal 'gong dang yi dwags zhugs pa dang /
NK041(di)023:602: gza' skar ngan pa la shi ba dang /
NK041(di)023:603: lus srog dbang thang gud pa dang /
NK041(di)023:604: rlung rta la dgra dar ba dang /
NK041(di)023:606: sri'u dang nad pa cis kyang ma sos pa sogs
NK041(di)023:607: mdor na mi mthun pa'i 'gal rkyen sel ba sogs
NK041(di)023:608: phan yon bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa
NK041(di)023:609: yin no // deng sang brgya bzhi'i cho ga shin tu dar ba ltar snang yang /
NK041(di)023:610: 'ga' zhig 'chi bslu dang ma mo'i glud chog sogs
NK041(di)023:611: kyang sbyar ba'i ngag 'don mang ba tsam snying por
NK041(di)023:612: bya ba dang / la las tshigs bcad sor sdebs nyung du tsam la bsdus pa sogs /
NK041(di)023:613: yig rnying lhad med rang sor gnas pa shin tu
NK041(di)023:614: dkon pas khungs thub kyi yid brtan dka' bar gyur
NK041(di)023:615: na'ang / yig snying gi sgrom gzhung sdebs pa na /
NK041(di)023:616: bar skabs so sor 'bri bsnan gyi dri ma ngos
NK041(di)023:617: zin pa ltar snang ba rnams dag par byas te
NK041(di)023:618: / bklags chog tu bkod pa yang /
NK041(di)023:619: deng dus 'di tsam la khungs ldan du rlom pa yin no //
NK041(di)023:620: de ltar brgya bzhi'i cho ga 'dod don lhun grub ces bya ba 'di yang /
NK041(di)023:621: cho ga 'di'i lag len du byed pa rnams la phan pa'i bsam pa dang /
NK041(di)023:622: dge sbyong 'tsho byed gzhan phan mchog sbyin gyis bskul
NK041(di)023:623: bas kyang rkyen byas te snyoms las pa 'gyur med
NK041(di)023:626: lha bdud dang gtor ma shar /
NK041(di)023:627: nyon bdud dang mar me nub /
NK041(di)023:628: 'chi bdud dang glud lan chags lho /
